processlink to cdr home cdr project processlink is a subproject of design space colonization and a follow on to the next link project objective our objective is to enable multidisciplinary design engineers to track and coordinate their design decisions with each other even when not co located or working with the same software approach agent based concurrent design integrating heterogeneous software is not enough not only are such integrations typically ad hoc and difficult to maintain but they do not solve the problem of who should be notified under what cicurmstances in the abcd approach this is done by agents that understand the engineering design process and can coordinate it technical overview recommended agents resource cdr home dsc home staff talks papers charles petrie last modified fri jan 28 14 37 35 pst 2000
